# EEE4113F_Group12_PCB - KiCAD files
## Overview
This PCB was eventually sent to [JLCPCB](https://jlcpcb.com/) for printing.

## What is included
This repository includes:
- The Project file
- The Schematic file
- The PCB file
Apologies for the files being so messy.

None of the generated gerber files are included.

## Installation & Dependencies
The files were made with KiCAD 9.0, so the same or a later version of KiCAD is needed to open the files.
